                    <msContents>
                        <summary><title type="supplied">The Provincial Law of Skåne and the Church
                                Law of Skåne</title>. The manuscript contains the Provincial Law of
                            Skåne ('Skånske lov'), the Church Law of Skåne ('Skånske kirkeret') as
                            well as a fragment of a literary text, a Danish translation of
                                'Contentio inter animam et corpus', that is not
                            contemporary with the law texts.</summary>
                        <textLang mainLang="da">Old Danish</textLang>
